{
  "texts": [
    "Ongoing work aims to reduce this overhead through model compression.",
    "The MCN-BERT model is a variant of the BERT model that uses a multi-layer self-attention mechanism to model the relationships between different parts of a sequence.",
    "The AdamP optimizer is a popular stochastic gradient descent algorithm that adapts the learning rate for each parameter based on the magnitude of the gradient.",
    "• Improved performance The MCN-BERT model has been shown to achieve state-of-the-art results on several natural language processing tasks.",
    "• Adaptive learning rate The AdamP optimizer adapts the learning rate for each parameter based on the mag- nitude of the gradient, which can help to converge faster and avoid getting stuck in local minima."
  ]
}